cs&amp;feature=c4-overview-vl&amp;list=PLF5551D055791D2A5"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1NSgPzYJzcs&amp;feature=c4-overview-vl&amp;list=PLF5551D055791D2A5</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn25"></a><a href="#_ednref25">[25]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> The Common Sense Alliance: Supporters. Accessed at, </span><a href="http://thecommonsensealliance.com/supporters/founding-members/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://thecommonsensealliance.com/supporters/founding-members/</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn26"></a><a href="#_ednref26">[26]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt">University of Bath: Tobacco Control Research Group; Tobacco Tactics;  </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">The Common Sense Alliance;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> Available at, </span><a href="http://www.tobaccotactics.org/index.php/The_Common_Sense_Alliance#.27Evidence.E2.80.99_presented_to_the_House_of_Lords_.E2.80.93_No_Mention_of_the_Alliance"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.tobaccotactics.org/index.php/The_Common_Sense_Alliance#.27Evidence.E2.80.99_presented_to_the_House_of_Lords_.E2.80.93_No_Mention_of_the_Alliance</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_edn27"></a><a href="#_ednref27">[27]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> Jamie Doward; Plain packaging lobbyists under fire over links to tobacco company; The Observer. 28 April 2013. Available at, </span><a href="http://www.theguardian.com/business/2013/apr/28/plain-packaging-lobbyists-links-tobac